title: [Yegharren Valley, Forest]
description: A moss-covered boulder as big as a house blocks the path to the east, its face covered with a network of fragile climbing vines.  An occasional faint buzzing breaks the silence of the night, its source a huge grey wasp nest suspended from a branch high above.
